# Images & Media

## Storefront ratios

| Surface | Aspect | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| Product cards | 1:1 or 4:5 | Real product/context; warm light |
| Blog thumbs | 16:9 | |
| Hero | Full-bleed crop | One LCP `priority` image max |

```tsx
// ✅ sized parent prevents CLS
<div className="relative aspect-square">
  <Image src={url} alt={`${name} gift`} fill sizes="(max-width:768px) 50vw, 25vw" />
</div>
```

- Empty `alt` only when decorative.
- No abstract purple-gradient “product” heroes.

## Platform

| Store | Holds |
|---|---|
| S3-compatible | Bytes |
| Postgres | Metadata, keys, dimensions, MIME — **not** BYTEA/base64 |

- Validate MIME + size at upload; reject executables/polyglots.
- Private assets → **signed URLs** with expiry (never permanent public ACL for private).
- Variants (thumb/web) via BullMQ when needed — don’t block request path on heavy transforms.

## Don't

Hotlink unsigned private objects from the browser. Ship unsized `<img>` that shove layout.
